  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Levi Hotel Spa is on a half board basis.</p>
<p>Each day fuel up for the day at the breakfast buffet served at the <span>Kekäle </span>restaurant, where you'll have the choice of a variety of hot and cold options, including traditional Lappish dishes and the standard continental offering.</p>
<p>Dinner is served buffet style until 8pm, which includes a choice of starter, main and dessert produced with season ingredients. Alternatively you can choose to dine à la carte and receive a €10 per adult or €5 per child, credit towards the meal. </p>
<p>There is a variety of restaurants  on site, including <span>Kekäle which serves fine dining Nordic dishes, Classic Pizza Restaurant and Burger King. These are not included within the package, but are great options if you fancy treating yourself to a meal out or want a quick lunch.</span></p>]]></cateringDescription>
