  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Ideally located in a central yet peaceful location, the Levi Hotel Spa is an excellent choice for families. <a data-udi="umb://document/9dee14339770490983c23ccc11530d35" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9dee14339770490983c23ccc11530d35}" title="Santa Breaks in Levi">Levi's</a> flagship property. With a range of family friendly facilities including the Spa Water World, fitness room and variety of restaurants, this hotel ticks all the boxes for a winter escape.</span></p>
<h2>Central location</h2>
<p><span>The village centre is a 3 minutes' walk (300m), where you can find a range of bars with live music, cosy cafes, restaurants and shops selling traditional Lappish souvenirs. Levitunturi is nearby, so you can make the most of the winter wonderland and snow covered fells, the slopes are also a short walk away making this a perfect choice for any guest considering our <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lapland-holidays/santa-breaks/resorts/laplandfinland/santa-breaks-in-levi#0" data-anchor="#0">ski taster</a> session during their <a data-udi="umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a}" title="Santa Breaks">Santa Break.</a></span></p>
<h2>Family friendly </h2>
<p><span>Families can enjoy an abundance of facilities on-site. Entrance to Spa Water World is included in your stay, with seventeen indoor and outdoor pools, waterslides, plus nine sauna/ steam rooms- the whole family will be entertained.  For the adults there's also a gym, yoga studio and Spa for various treatments which are available to book and pay for locally. Children can visit the children's play area, think little igloos with a TV, a big foam pit and other fun activities, it is a great spot to meet new friends. </span></p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
